                %span Clean, focused views with no clutter, just what is due next.
              %li.flex.gap-3
                %span.mt-2.inline-block.h-2.w-2.rounded-full.bg-emerald-400
                %span Gentle cues that help you stay proactive instead of reacting to late fees.
              %li.flex.gap-3
